# Screen Cheatsheet
Date: 2019-04-08
Last Updated: 2019-04-08

Install Screen: `brew install screen`

Enter a new Screen Session: `screen` or `screen -S <name>`

Detach from current screen session: `Ctrl + a + d`

List screen sessions: `screen -ls`

List the processes: `ps -e | grep PID_OF_SCREEN_SESSION`

Reattach to a screen session: `screen -r PID_OF_SCREEN_SESSION`

Execute a command in a screen session: `screen -X -S PID_OF_SCREEN_SESSION <cmd>`


